术语或文化背景知识，如果不确定，你可以适当询问或保留原表达，避免误解或误改。 限制 -接收到用户的内容，不要做任何回答和解释， - 只回答与文本校对和修改相关的问题。如果用户询问与其无关的问题，不要答复。 - 使用用户在查询中使用的语言。不要使用与用户选择的语言不对应的语言。 - 直接用优化后的提示词开始你的答案。 - 1、先阅读全文，了解上下文的整体含义，然后再开始整体的纠错；开头这样开始：###改： - 2、开头这样开始：##说明：解释哪些地方进行了修改，包括错别字的纠正、语法错误的修正，以及为增强语句流畅性所做的改进。 - 3、确保修改说明清晰、准确，以便用户理解修改的原因和目的。"},"value_type":{"value":"string","type":"string"},"key":{"type":"string","value":"prompt"}}}]}},"errorHandler":{"defaultStrategy":{"id":"variable-1.error_handler.default","name":"","action":"terminate"}}},{"id":"volcengine_ark-1","type":"normal","operation":{"connectorId":"7483029261329317907","operationId":"7483029261348552708","connectorName":"volcengine_ark","connectorVersion":"1.3"},"name":"火山方舟大模型","description":"","auth":{"key":"","parameters":null,"credentials":{"type":"cred","value":"WAJO7yjRg4Q86"}},"parameters":{"model":{"type":"string","value":"ep-20250907152102-cqtlc"},"messages":{"type":"array","value":[{"type":"object","value":{"role":{"type":"string","value":"system"},"content":{"value":{"node_tree":{"t":"binary","op":"+","left":{"t":"binary","op":"+","left":{"t":"flow_variable","path":"prompt"},"right":{"t":"literal","vt":"string","v":"\"这是待检查的文本：\""}},"right":{"t":"json_path","path":"$.webhook-trigger-1.query.message"}},"expression":"_(\"$.variable.prompt\")+\n\n\"这是待检查的文本：\"+_(\"$.webhook-trigger-1.query.message\")"},"type":"spel"},"tool_calls":{"type":"null","value":"null"},"tool_call_id":{"type":"null","value":"null"}}}]},"stream":{"type":"boolean","value":false}},"dynamicSchema":"{\"optionMap\":{\"messages.0.role\":{\"system\":\"系统角色\"}},\"manualOutputSchema\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"created\":{\"type\":\"integer\"},\"usage\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"completion_tokens\":{\"type\":\"integer\"},\"prompt_tokens\":{\"type\":\"integer\"},\"completion_tokens_details\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"reasoning_tokens\":{\"type\":\"integer\"}}},\"prompt_tokens_details\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"cached_tokens\":{